data.description: Beautifully remodeled home that features the following: 4 bed/3 bath, new flooring, new paint, new Kitchen with new quartz countertops and all new appliances as well as new gorgeous custom built cabinets and a new Furnace. The primary bedroom has a walk-in closet that is literally the size of a small bedroom. There is a living room, a den and a separate dining area. This home has over 3900 square feet and is move-in ready. It sits on a 1 acre parcel with shade trees and a large gazebo space to enjoy all of the outdoor parties you want to have. Attached is a one car garage and a large detached garage with a carport, plus another shed for additional storage space. Don't miss this one!
